verses.text: Unto \w the|strong="H1732"\w* end, \w for|strong="H1732"\w* them \w that|strong="H1732"\w* \w shall|strong="H1732"\w* \w be|strong="H1732"\w* changed; \w for|strong="H1732"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*.

\w SAVE|strong="H5127"\w* \w me|strong="H6440"\w*, \w O|strong="H0430"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*: \w for|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* waters \w are|strong="H0430"\w* \w come|strong="H6965"\w* \w in|strong="H0430"\w* even unto \w my|strong="H6965"\w* soul.

I stick fast \w in|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* mire \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* deep: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* there \w is|strong="H0430"\w* \w no|strong="H0006"\w* sure standing. I \w am|strong="H0430"\w* come into \w the|strong="H6440"\w* depth \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* sea: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w a|strong="H6440"\w* tempest hath overwhelmed \w me|strong="H6440"\w*.

\w I|strong="H7797"\w* \w have|strong="H0430"\w* laboured \w with|strong="H0430"\w* crying; \w my|strong="H6440"\w* jaws \w are|strong="H0430"\w* become hoarse: \w my|strong="H6440"\w* \w eyes|strong="H8055"\w* \w have|strong="H0430"\w* failed, whilst \w I|strong="H7797"\w* hope \w in|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H6440"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*.

\w They|strong="H0430"\w* \w are|strong="H0430"\w* multiplied \w above|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* hairs \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H6440"\w* \w head|strong="H6440"\w*, \w who|strong="H0430"\w* hate \w me|strong="H6440"\w* without \w cause|strong="H7392"\w*. \w My|strong="H6440"\w* enemies \w are|strong="H0430"\w* grown strong \w who|strong="H0430"\w* \w have|strong="H8034"\w* wrongfully persecuted \w me|strong="H6440"\w*: then did \w I|strong="H8034"\w* pay \w that|strong="H0430"\w* which \w I|strong="H8034"\w* \w took|strong="H7392"\w* not away.

\w O|strong="H0430"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w*, thou knowest \w my|strong="H0430"\w* foolishness; \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H0430"\w* offences \w are|strong="H0430"\w* not hidden \w from|strong="H0430"\w* thee:

\w Let|strong="H0389"\w* not \w them|strong="H3318"\w* \w be|strong="H0430"\w* ashamed \w for|strong="H1004"\w* \w me|strong="H3318"\w*, \w who|strong="H3427"\w* look \w for|strong="H1004"\w* thee, \w O|strong="H1004"\w* Lord, \w the|strong="H3318"\w* Lord \w of|strong="H1004"\w* hosts. \w Let|strong="H0389"\w* \w them|strong="H3318"\w* not \w be|strong="H0430"\w* confounded \w on|strong="H3427"\w* \w my|strong="H3318"\w* account, \w who|strong="H3427"\w* seek thee, \w O|strong="H1004"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w of|strong="H1004"\w* Israel.
\w Because|strong="H6440"\w* \w for|strong="H0430"\w* thy sake I \w have|strong="H0430"\w* borne reproach; shame hath covered \w my|strong="H3318"\w* \w face|strong="H6440"\w*.

\w I|strong="H2088"\w* \w am|strong="H0430"\w* become \w a|strong="H2088"\w* stranger \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w my|strong="H2088"\w* brethren, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w an|strong="H6440"\w* alien \w to|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* sons \w of|strong="H0776"\w* \w my|strong="H2088"\w* mother.

\w For|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* zeal \w of|strong="H0430"\w* thy house hath eaten \w me|strong="H0859"\w* up: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H3559"\w* reproaches \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w them|strong="H0859"\w* \w that|strong="H3559"\w* reproached thee \w are|strong="H0430"\w* fallen upon \w me|strong="H0859"\w*.

\w And|strong="H0430"\w* \w I|strong="H3559"\w* covered \w my|strong="H3559"\w* soul \w in|strong="H3427"\w* fasting: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w it|strong="H3559"\w* \w was|strong="H0430"\w* \w made|strong="H3559"\w* \w a|strong="H3559"\w* reproach \w to|strong="H0430"\w* \w me|strong="H2416"\w*.

\w And|strong="H6635"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* \w made|strong="H5414"\w* haircloth \w my|strong="H5414"\w* garment: \w and|strong="H6635"\w* \w I|strong="H5414"\w* became \w a|strong="H5414"\w* byword \w to|strong="H5414"\w* \w them|strong="H5414"\w*.

\w They|strong="H4428"\w* \w that|strong="H1004"\w* sat \w in|strong="H1004"\w* \w the|strong="H1004"\w* gate spoke against \w me|strong="H1004"\w*: \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w they|strong="H4428"\w* \w that|strong="H1004"\w* drank wine made \w me|strong="H1004"\w* their song.

\w But|strong="H0518"\w* \w as|strong="H3701"\w* \w for|strong="H0518"\w* me, \w my|strong="H0996"\w* prayer \w is|strong="H3701"\w* \w to|strong="H3701"\w* thee, \w O|strong="H0518"\w* Lord; \w for|strong="H0518"\w* \w the|strong="H0996"\w* time \w of|strong="H3671"\w* thy good pleasure, \w O|strong="H0518"\w* God. \w In|strong="H7901"\w* \w the|strong="H0996"\w* multitude \w of|strong="H3671"\w* thy mercy hear me, \w in|strong="H7901"\w* \w the|strong="H0996"\w* truth \w of|strong="H3671"\w* thy salvation.

Draw me \w out|strong="H6566"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H6566"\w* mire, \w that|strong="H4428"\w* \w I|strong="H6566"\w* \w may|strong="H4428"\w* not stick fast: deliver me \w from|strong="H4428"\w* them \w that|strong="H4428"\w* hate me, \w and|strong="H4428"\w* \w out|strong="H6566"\w* \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w the|strong="H6566"\w* deep waters.

Let not \w the|strong="H0430"\w* tempest \w of|strong="H0430"\w* water drown me, nor \w the|strong="H0430"\w* deep swallow me up: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* let not \w the|strong="H0430"\w* pit shut her mouth upon me.

Hear \w me|strong="H4100"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*, \w for|strong="H3068"\w* thy \w mercy|strong="H3068"\w* \w is|strong="H3068"\w* kind; \w look|strong="H7520"\w* \w upon|strong="H3427"\w* \w me|strong="H4100"\w* according \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* multitude \w of|strong="H0430"\w* thy tender mercies.

\w And|strong="H0430"\w* turn not away thy face \w from|strong="H0430"\w* thy servant: \w for|strong="H0430"\w* \w I|strong="H7393"\w* \w am|strong="H0430"\w* \w in|strong="H0430"\w* trouble, hear me speedily.

Attend \w to|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* soul, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* deliver \w it|strong="H3947"\w*: save \w me|strong="H3947"\w* because \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H3947"\w* enemies.
Thou knowest \w my|strong="H0136"\w* reproach, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w my|strong="H0136"\w* confusion, \w and|strong="H3117"\w* \w my|strong="H0136"\w* shame.

\w In|strong="H0410"\w* thy sight are all they \w that|strong="H0136"\w* afflict me; \w my|strong="H0136"\w* heart hath expected reproach \w and|strong="H4194"\w* misery. \w And|strong="H4194"\w* I looked \w for|strong="H4194"\w* \w one|strong="H0410"\w* \w that|strong="H0136"\w* would grieve together with me, but there \w was|strong="H0136"\w* none: \w and|strong="H4194"\w* \w for|strong="H4194"\w* \w one|strong="H0410"\w* \w that|strong="H0136"\w* would comfort me, \w and|strong="H4194"\w* I found none.

\w And|strong="H1980"\w* \w they|strong="H0430"\w* gave \w me|strong="H1980"\w* gall \w for|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H0430"\w* food, \w and|strong="H1980"\w* \w in|strong="H1980"\w* \w my|strong="H0430"\w* thirst \w they|strong="H0430"\w* gave \w me|strong="H1980"\w* vinegar \w to|strong="H1980"\w* drink.

Let \w their|strong="H7725"\w* table \w become|strong="H7725"\w* \w as|strong="H1316"\w* \w a|strong="H7725"\w* snare before \w them|strong="H7725"\w*, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w a|strong="H7725"\w* \w recompense|strong="H7725"\w*, \w and|strong="H7725"\w* \w a|strong="H7725"\w* stumblingblock.

Let \w their|strong="H4480"\w* eyes \w be|strong="H4480"\w* darkened \w that|strong="H4616"\w* \w they|strong="H3611"\w* see not; \w and|strong="H1818"\w* \w their|strong="H4480"\w* back bend thou down always.

Pour \w out|strong="H7200"\w* thy indignation \w upon|strong="H7200"\w* \w them|strong="H7200"\w*: \w and|strong="H0430"\w* let thy wrathful anger \w take|strong="H7200"\w* hold \w of|strong="H4428"\w* \w them|strong="H7200"\w*.

Let \w their|strong="H0310"\w* habitation be made desolate: \w and|strong="H0310"\w* let \w there|strong="H8432"\w* be none \w to|strong="H7891"\w* dwell \w in|strong="H8432"\w* \w their|strong="H0310"\w* tabernacles.

Because \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* persecuted \w him|strong="H1288"\w* whom thou hast smitten; \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* added \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* grief \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* wounds.
Add thou iniquity upon \w their|strong="H8033"\w* iniquity: \w and|strong="H3063"\w* let them not come \w into|strong="H3063"\w* thy justice.

Let \w them|strong="H6680"\w* \w be|strong="H0430"\w* blotted \w out|strong="H6466"\w* \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6680"\w* book \w of|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6680"\w* living; \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w with|strong="H0430"\w* \w the|strong="H6680"\w* just let \w them|strong="H6680"\w* not \w be|strong="H0430"\w* written.
\w But|strong="H4428"\w* \w I|strong="H5921"\w* am poor \w and|strong="H4428"\w* sorrowful: thy salvation, O God, hath set \w me|strong="H5921"\w* \w up|strong="H5921"\w*.

\w I|strong="H0047"\w* \w will|strong="H5695"\w* praise \w the|strong="H1605"\w* name \w of|strong="H5712"\w* \w God|strong="H0967"\w* \w with|strong="H7070"\w* \w a|strong="H3701"\w* canticle: \w and|strong="H3701"\w* \w I|strong="H0047"\w* \w will|strong="H5695"\w* magnify him \w with|strong="H7070"\w* praise.

\w And|strong="H0430"\w* it \w shall|strong="H4714"\w* please \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w better|strong="H3027"\w* \w than|strong="H4480"\w* \w a|strong="H4480"\w* young calf, \w that|strong="H4480"\w* bringeth forth horns \w and|strong="H0430"\w* hoofs.
Let \w the|strong="H0776"\w* poor see \w and|strong="H0430"\w* rejoice: seek ye \w God|strong="H0430"\w*, \w and|strong="H0430"\w* \w your|strong="H0430"\w* soul \w shall|strong="H0776"\w* live.
\w For|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* Lord hath \w heard|strong="H6963"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* poor: \w and|strong="H8064"\w* hath not despised \w his|strong="H5414"\w* prisoners.

\w Let|strong="H5414"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* heavens \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H5921"\w* earth praise \w him|strong="H5414"\w*; \w the|strong="H5921"\w* sea, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* every thing \w that|strong="H3478"\w* creepeth therein.

\w For|strong="H0430"\w* \w God|strong="H0430"\w* \w will|strong="H0430"\w* save Sion, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* cities \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Juda \w shall|strong="H3478"\w* \w be|strong="H1288"\w* built \w up|strong="H5414"\w*. \w And|strong="H3478"\w* \w they|strong="H5971"\w* \w shall|strong="H3478"\w* dwell there, \w and|strong="H3478"\w* acquire \w it|strong="H5414"\w* \w by|strong="H3478"\w* inheritance.
And the seed of his servants shall possess it; and they that love his name shall dwell therein.
